<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Buoina him him a um kha puoi,
 Thagau khawvel gamnuom achun,
 Tatte chamtatna gamnuom chu,
 Zie lei mun bang hi a hi puoi,

[V2]
 Lungkhamna leh gimtheihnan ei bawm,
 Buoina te'n tuilien bangin ei tawk
 Kipahna la sang ka a chungah,
 Bit takin van gam ei tun ina.

[V3]
 2. Leia munnuom kei di'n ahak,
 Gimthei thuoka ka kahna phet,
 Ziemun nuom chu vatung ta leng,
 Kipahna mun ka chang deimawh.

[V4]
 3. Hukdmpa mihing hih lai khan,
 &quot;Umna tamtak a um&quot; A tii,
 Ka chan ding dawl umlo ahim?
 Tia ngaiin ka thil chim puoi,

[V5]
 4. Zie khawvela ka khensa te'n
 Ei uou ui lui gal lehlam ah,
 &quot;Hungkai inla kivawp khawm din,&quot;
 Khut zak sieu sieu in a tiu hi.

[V6]
 5. Aw na lul ie thisan lopi,
 Nangmah vangin gimthei chate;
 Zie mun nuom chu a tung zo tau,
 Tuhin le a chieh nalai ui.</lyrics>
<title>Thagau Khawvel Ah</title>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>178</hymn_number>
</song>